OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny intervals through much of
OL,6,Fthe day, before cloud thickens up into
OL,7,Fthe evening with one or two showers
OL,8,Fpossible. Breezy at times,
OL,9,Fparticularly on eastern coasts, where
OL,10,Fthere will be a cooler feel to the day.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy for much of the period
OL,13,Fwith clear spells developing late in
OL,14,Fthe night. Isolated evening showers
OL,15,Fclearing, leaving a largely dry night.
OL,16,FFeeling cool in brisk northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
