OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FSunny spells for many,
OL,6,Fthough cooler than recent days.
OL,7,FLargely dry with occasional showers
OL,8,Faffecting Kent. Breezy, especially
OL,9,Falong coasts. Chilly overnight with
OL,10,Fisolated rural frosts possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FThursday brings sunny spells and the
OL,14,Fodd shower. Conditions turn more
OL,15,Funsettled Friday and Saturday with
OL,16,Fspells of rain or showers,
OL,17,Foccasionally heavy. At times cool,
OL,18,Fwith isolated frosts overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
